                              Disk Catalogue V2
                              ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    
þ
        An extremely simple disk cataloguing program, which stores all the
    contents of lots of disks. It stores the information by asking for a
    disk number, and you entering information on that disk, which is then
    instantly loadable, and displayed on-screen. A much better version
    will be released very soon.
    
