                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    
þ
        A small CLI utility which will allow you to listen to any AMOS
    music or tracker bank, OctaMED module, or any Sound/Pro/Noisetracker
    module whilst you are working on something in Workbench. The program
    loses no processor time, as it is fully CLI automated.
    
    
